{@st59b} Diário de Aventuras {nl}{@st59s}- Your game progress is recorded in the Adventure Journal. {nl} - You can progress your Adventure Index through contents such as: obtaining items, hunting monsters, crafting and map exploration.{nl}    Adventure Index : The total of all your indexes. {nl}    Growth : 5 points per character level and class level {nl}    Items : Equipment : grade X 10 points, Books : 10 points, Others : 1 point {nl}    Monsters : 10 points per monster (50 points for Boss Monsters) {nl}    Maps : 1 point per 10% explored {nl}    Quests : 1 point per quest {nl}    Achievements : Varies by achievement {nl}    Crafting : 10 points {nl}    Coleção : 5 points for a deck and 45 points when it is Completod {nl} - You can receive special rewards from an NPC in town depending on your Adventure Index. {/}

{@st59b}Transcend Item{nl}{@st59s}- Another way to enhance the item's performance other than by the anvil{nl}- Items that can transcend : Weapons, armor and accessories{nl}- Transcendence Success Rate = Used Ingredients / Maximum Required Ingredients{nl}- Increases Transcendence Stage by 1 on success (Maximum of 10 Stages){nl}- Decreases Transcendence Stage by 1 on failure (No Potential loss){nl}- Transcended items cannot be traded{/}

{@st59b}Extract Blessed Gem{nl}{@st59s}- Extract Blessed Gem from transcended items{nl}- Extraction Requirements : Hammer of Dismantlement{nl}- You'll Receber some of the Blessed Gems used for Transcendence even though the item will be destroyed. {nl}- You cannot do this at Transcendence Stage 0.{/}
{@st59b}Extract Item{nl}{@st59s}- Remove the transcendental effects from a transcended item{nl}- Extraction Requirements : Spell Rod{/}

{@st59b}Item Transcendence{nl}{@st59s}- Enhances an item's performance in a way different from the anvil enhancement{nl}- Transcendables : Weapon, Armor, Accessory{nl}- Transcendence Chance = Amount of Ingredients / Required Minimum{nl}- If successful, Transcendence level increases by 1(Max. 10){nl}- If failed, Transcendence level along with potential by 1(Transcendence level does not go below 1){nl}- Transcended Item Cannot Be Traded{/}

{@st59b}Blessed Gem Extraction{nl}{@st59s}- Extracting Blessed Gems from Transcended Items{nl}- Ingredient for Blessed Gem Extraction : Hammer of Dismantlement{nl}- A portion of Blessed Gems used on the item can be refunded. {nl}   : Depending on the current transcendence level and remaining potential, the refund rate is minimum 20% to maximum 90%. {nl}- Cannot be used on Transcendence Level 0.{/}
Deseja utilizar o Rank Reset Voucher?
O item desaparecerá do seu inventário{nl}e suas opções Rank serão redefinidas.
* As Cartas de Monstros equipadas serão automaticamente{nl}removidos sem penalidades..
* Níveis de atributo comprados antes do reset{nl}podem ser aprendidos novamente sem nenhum custo após o reset.
* EXP cards equivalent to the last Rank to have achieved{nl}
will be provided to your inventory.
* Trajes específicos de classe recebidos{nl}por avanço de Rank serão excluídos.
* You will return to the barracks after using the Voucher.
{@st59}Pesquisar o nome de uma coleção ou efeito.{/}

{@st59b}Blessed Gem Extraction{nl}{@st59s}- Extracts Blessed Gems from transcended items.{nl}- Materials needed: Hammer of Dismantlement.{nl}- Extracting Blessed Gems will delete the item, but retain part of the gems. {nl}   : You will receive 20% to 90% of the Blessed Gems, depending on the item's transcendence stage and current potential. {nl}- Your item must be transcended to at least stage 2 in order to extract the gems.{/}
